msgstr "`io.quarkus.sbom.Purl` - 使用 link:https://github.com/package-url/purl-spec[软件包 URL] 规范识别软件组件。为 Maven、npm 和通用组件类型提供了工厂方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/cyclonedx.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`io.quarkus.sbom.ComponentDescriptor` — describes a software component with its PURL, scope, integrity hash, and other metadata."
msgstr "`io.quarkus.sbom.ComponentDescriptor` - 用 PURL、范围、完整性哈希值和其他元数据描述软件组件。"

#. type: Plain text
